The paper deals with the problem of comparing and summarizing documents, which is a common task in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed solution uses a graph-based framework and optimization techniques, which are common in machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
